Description
AccessType
Access type as in CRUD CREATE, READ, UPDATE or DELETE Corresponds to POST, GET, PUT and DELETE methods of HTTP

BadRequest
The 400 Bad Request HTTP error status
BasicDao
A data access object for a table representing an EasyModel class Each method performs a different database query
BelongsTo
One side of a one-to-one or one-to-many association.
BelongsToDao
Data access object for performing database queries on associations where one side of the association is a BelongsTo association.
Controller
A mapping between HTTP requests and actions performed by the model
EasyController
A controller for EasyModel models
EasyModel
Base class for a model in a Rest Easy application
EasyView

HasMany

HasOne
One side of a many-to-one association.
HttpController
A mapping between the four main HTTP verbs and the more specific versions specified by the Controller interface.
HttpErrorStatus
An error in an HTTP request
InternalServerError
The 500 Internal Server Error HTTP error status
JoinTableDao
Data access object for performing database queries on many-to-many associations.
Loader
Utility class to search for subclasses of EasyModel in the classpath
NoHttp

NoPersist

ServletController
